191
00:16:36,050 --> 00:16:37,130
All these years,

192
00:16:37,260 --> 00:16:37,530
No.

193
00:16:37,560 --> 00:16:38,890
you only care about her.

194
00:16:42,630 --> 00:16:43,230
Alright.

195
00:16:44,660 --> 00:16:45,900
