230
00:19:34,230 --> 00:19:35,830
people's thoughts and love.

231
00:19:40,970 --> 00:19:42,850
I've missed Boya's love.

232
00:19:43,500 --> 00:19:44,900
I don't want to

233
00:19:45,920 --> 00:19:49,120
