259
00:21:08,910 --> 00:21:09,750
I need to go.

260
00:21:11,630 --> 00:21:13,030
I wish you happiness too.

261
00:21:22,050 --> 00:21:22,780
Bye.

262
00:21:50,730 --> 00:21:51,530
